skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: number race
des: This is a simple educational math game: two player take turns to count from 1 to 30, at each turn, a player can only count one or two numbers consecutively. Whoever reaches 30 wins. Game instruction is included in the skill
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
